---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="China-EU-US EV/Battery Policy Timeline Tables (Free Download)"
  description="Free download of 173 EV/battery policy timeline comparison tables across China, EU, and US. Covering 1986-2026. Open community contribution."
  lang="en"
  path="/en/policy-tables/"
>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:120px;padding-bottom:60px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:linear-gradient(160deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #ffffff 40%, #eef1f5 100%);">
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-3xl);">
      <p class="section-label" style="color:var(--color-accent);">Free Resource · Open Community</p>
      <h1 style="max-width:750px;margin:0 auto var(--spacing-md);font-size:2.4rem;">
        China-EU-US EV & Battery Policy Timeline Comparison Tables
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto var(--spacing-lg);font-weight:500;">
        Spanning 1986–2026 — China 71 + EU 42 + USA 61 policies
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-muted);max-width:500px;margin:0 auto;">
        Version Rev.1 (2026-05-04)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="background:var(--color-surface);padding-top:var(--spacing-3xl);padding-bottom:var(--spacing-3xl);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-3" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-3xl);">
      <div class="service-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:40px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">📊</div>
        <h4>6-Column Standard Format</h4>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">No. | Date | Policy Name | Issuer | Core Content | Source</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:40px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">🌐</div>
        <h4>Bilingual (CN/EN)</h4>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Every table available in both Chinese and English</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:40px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">🔄</div>
        <h4>Continuously Updated</h4>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Community corrections and additions welcome. New versions released regularly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-2xl);">Download Tables</h2>
    
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:var(--spacing-lg);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-2xl);">
      <div style="padding:var(--spacing-lg);background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FEF3C7,#FFFBEB);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #FDE68A;text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">🇨🇳</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;">China NEV & ICV</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">863 Plan (1986) → 2026.04</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">71 policies</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-sm);justify-content:center;">
          <a href="/files/China_NEV_policy_table_CN.docx" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;background:#B45309;">中文版</a>
          <a href="/files/China_NEV_policy_table_EN.docx" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;border-color:#B45309;color:#B45309;">English</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:var(--spacing-lg);background:linear-gradient(135deg,#DBEAFE,#EFF6FF);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #93C5FD;text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">🇪🇺</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;">EU EV · Battery · CBAM</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">Fit for 55 → CBAM carbon collection (2026.01)</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">42 policies</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-sm);justify-content:center;">
          <a href="/files/EU_NEV_policy_table_CN.docx" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;background:#1D4ED8;">中文版</a>
          <a href="/files/EU_NEV_policy_table_EN.docx" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;border-color:#1D4ED8;color:#1D4ED8;">English</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:var(--spacing-lg);background:linear-gradient(135deg,#DCFCE7,#F0FDF4);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #86EFAC;text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">🇺🇸</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;">USA EV · Battery · Charging</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">IRA → CHIPS → Trump reversal → OBBB repeal</p>
        <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">61 policies</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-sm);justify-content:center;">
          <a href="/files/US_NEV_policy_table_CN.docx" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;background:#15803D;">中文版</a>
          <a href="/files/US_NEV_policy_table_EN.docx" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;border-color:#15803D;color:#15803D;">English</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center" style="margin:var(--spacing-2xl) 0;padding:var(--spacing-xl);background:var(--color-surface);border:2px dashed var(--color-accent);border-radius:12px;">
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);">Get all 6 tables (Word format) in one go</p>
      <a href="mailto:policy@humanaifit.com?subject=Policy Tables Download" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:14px 36px;font-size:15px;">Email to Request All Tables</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin:var(--spacing-3xl) 0;padding:var(--spacing-xl);background:#FFF7ED;border:1px solid #FDDCBA;border-radius:12px;">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);">
        <p class="section-label" style="color:#C2410C;">Open Community Contribution</p>
        <h2>Help Us Find Gaps & Errors</h2>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);max-width:500px;margin:var(--spacing-sm) auto;">
          This is not a perfect table. If you find missing policies or errors, please let us know.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:var(--spacing-lg);">
        <div style="background:white;border-radius:8px;padding:var(--spacing-lg);border:1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <h4 style="font-size:1rem;">Submit GitHub Issue</h4>
          <a href="https://github.com/wolconniewu-art/humanaifit-website/issues/new" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;">Submit Issue</a>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white;border-radius:8px;padding:var(--spacing-lg);border:1px solid var(--color-border);">
          <h4 style="font-size:1rem;">Send Email</h4>
          <a href="mailto:policy@humanaifit.com?subject=Policy Tables Correction" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding:8px 16px;font-size:12px;">Send Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:var(--spacing-lg);">
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-muted);">
          The first 10 people to submit valid corrections will receive a free CBAM report
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-2xl);">Three Key Findings</h2>
    <div class="service-card" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);">
      <h4>China: 40 Years of Unbroken Policy Evolution</h4>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">1986 863 Plan → 2001 Three Verticals Three Horizontals → 2009 Ten Cities Thousand Vehicles → 2012 Pure Electric Drive → 2015 Dual Credit → 2025 ICV Integration. China offers the most sustained and systematic policy framework among the three nations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card" style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);">
      <h4>EU: 2026 is the Year of Enforcement</h4>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">2019 Green Deal → 2021 Fit for 55 → CBAM carbon collection (2026.01) → Battery carbon footprint label (2026.02). The EU is moving from legislation to enforcement.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <h4>USA: The World's Most Dramatic Policy Reversal</h4>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">2022 IRA (massive subsidies) → Jan 2025 Trump repeal of EV mandate → Jul 2025 OBBB repeal of tax credits. Three years from heaven to hell.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;">Is your product affected by CBAM?</h2>
    <p style="max-width:500px;margin:var(--spacing-md) auto var(--spacing-xl);font-size:15px;opacity:0.85;">
      Free self-check in 30 seconds.
    </p>
    <a href="https://cbam.humanaifit.com" class="btn btn-primary" style="background:#10B981;" target="_blank">Start CBAM Check</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>